    {\displaystyle w_{j};}
   such a convention is useful for avoiding errors in explicit computations.)
Setting 
  
    
      
        
          B
          
            
              n
              e
              w
            
          
        
        =
        (
        
          w
          
            1
          
        
        ,
        …
        ,
        
          w
          
            n
          
        
        )
