        i
        =
        1
        ,
        …
        ,
        n
        .
      
    
    {\displaystyle x_{i}=\sum _{j=1}^{n}a_{i,j}y_{j}\qquad {\text{for }}i=1,\ldots ,n.}
  In terms of matrices, the change of basis formula is

  
    
      
        
          x
        
        =
        A
        
        
          y
        
        ,
      
    
    {\displaystyle \mathbf {x} =A\,\mathbf {y} ,}
  where 
  
    
      
        
          x
        
      
    
